data.description: Fantastic opportunity single family home with 3320 sqft in ARTESA GATED COMMUNITY with 5 bedroom, 3,5 bathrooms. Split floor plan with NEXT GEN Suite with separate entrance 1 bedroom and 1 full bathroom, living & dinning room, washer and dryer, microwave, refrigerator and AC mini split. Is currently rented until September 30, 2024. In the main house on the first floor have half bathroom, big dinning and living room, dark wood ceiling high  Kitchen cabinets, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, a snack/ breakfast bar and open family room - great for entertaining!  Large primary bedroom with 2 generous walk-in closets. 2-car garage. Impact doors and windows. Club house with fitness center, pool, and playground. Very close to turnpike.
